item.title: From Molar Pregnancy, To C-Section, To Homebirth, To Doula with Suzzie Vehrs
item.description:
Hi I'm Suzzie, a doula and childbirth educator. 

Like many moms I had a turbulent entry to motherhood. First with a molar pregnancy and loss and then with an emergency c-section. 

These experiences left me feeling like birth was scary, hard and I didn't know enough to fully put into words the anxieties and worries that kept me up at night. 

By the time I had my second daughter a lot changed... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/f8f2f564/podcast/rss

item.title: Rich and Daily: Britney Claps Back at the Osbournes
item.description: Richies, it’s our last episode before we go on summer vacation, and we’ve got a juicy one for you. Britney Spears is clapping back at Ozzy Osbourne and the rest of his family. On a recent episode of the podcast, “The Osbournes,” Ozzy called Britney’s dance videos “very, very sad” and said he feels sorry for her. But the “Toxic” singer took to Instagram on Wednesday to fire back at all the Osbournes - and she didn’t mince words... Feed: https://rss.art19.com/even-the-rich
